{"to":["sarah@alumni.prestige.edu"],"subject":"Update on the New Admissions Cycle","body":"Hi Sarah,

I hope this message finds you well! I wanted to share some exciting updates regarding the new admissions cycle:

- This cycle has seen a 5% increase in applications, with a total of 15,000 applicants!
- The acceptance rate decreased to 7%, resulting in the admission of 1,050 exceptional students.
- Admitted students have an impressive average SAT score of 1480 and an average ACT score of 33.
- Students from over 60 different countries are part of this diverse new cohort.

If you're interested in further details, let me know. It's truly an exciting time for everyone involved!

All the best,

[Your Name]"}
